title: Talkin' MOB with Willis Kimbel
description: Where’s Willis Kimbel been?!… Ripping in Finland! Willis just joined the MOB Grip squad, and it’s without a doubt he’s been shredding Finland on the daily. Drop in with Willis at his local DIY in this installment of Talkin’ MOB. Willis skates for Creature Skateboards, Independent Trucks, MOB Grip, and OJ Wheels.
